  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Himachal Pradesh</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Himachal Pradesh experiences diverse climates across regions. Summer (April-June) brings pleasant weather with clear skies. Monsoon (July-September) brings lush greenery and occasional rainfall. Autumn (October-November) offers crisp air and panoramic views. Winter (December-March) brings snowfall in high altitude areas, creating a winter wonderland perfect for snow sports.</p>
